item.title: CVE-2023-5798|2024-08-02T08:14:24.078Z -- unknown -- assistant
item.description: The Assistant WordPress plugin before 1.4.4 does not validate a parameter before making a request to it via wp_remote_get(), which could allow users with a role as low as Editor to perform SSRF attacks
